<section id="srcLang">
    <title>srcLang</title>
    
    <para>Source language - the code of the language, in which the text to be <firstterm>Translated</firstterm> is
        expressed.</para>
    <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis><?oxy_custom_end?>
        string.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> a language code as described in <olink
            targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="bcp47">[BCP 47]</olink>.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/xliff.xml" targetptr="xliff"
                ><code><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>jliff<?oxy_custom_end?></code></olink>.</para>
